Usage: ecoDefIn [-help] <fileName> [-cleanFEData] [-ecoDef <fileName>]
                [-keepInstLoc] [-mergeFloatingRouteToPGNet <netName>]
                [-postMask] [-reportFile <fileName>] [-suffix <suffixVal>]
                [-useGACells <val>]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
<fileName>                               # file name (string, required)
-cleanFEData                             # clean FE data (bool, optional)
-ecoDef <fileName>                       # eco def fileName (string, optional)
-keepInstLoc                             # keep instance location
                                         # (bool, optional)
-mergeFloatingRouteToPGNet <netName>     # merge net name (string, optional)
-postMask                                # postmask suffix on (bool, optional)
-reportFile <fileName>                   # report file name (string, optional)
-suffix <suffixVal>                      # suffix string (string, optional)
-useGACells <val>                        # use GA cells (string, optional)